lead_paragraph: Two of English soccer's founder clubs meet in the second-tier Championship on Saturday, both gripped by turmoil and unsure of their future as foreign owners grapple with the problem of restoring their fortunes.

headline.print_headline: Rovers Meet Wolves in Clash of Fallen Giants
headline.main: Rovers Meet Wolves in Clash of Fallen Giants
